<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 18:13:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>一名女子因涉嫌从中国欺诈中洗钱 63 亿美元而在伦敦受审</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/woman-tried-london-over-alleged-bitcoin-laundering-63-bln-china-fraud-2024-01-29/</link><description>检察官周一告诉伦敦一家法院，一名女子将比特币兑换成现金和财产，以帮助洗钱在中国实施的 50 亿英镑（63 亿美元）欺诈案的收益。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 18:03:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/woman-tried-london-over-alleged-bitcoin-laundering-63-bln-china-fraud-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>议员们希望美国调查四家参与福特电池厂的中国公司——信函</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/lawmakers-want-us-probe-four-chinese-firms-involved-ford-battery-plant-letter-2024-01-29/</link><description>据路透社周一看到的一封信函，美国众议院两个委员会的主席要求拜登政府调查四家中国公司，他们称这些公司参与了福特汽车计划中的密歇根电池工厂。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 17:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/lawmakers-want-us-probe-four-chinese-firms-involved-ford-battery-plant-letter-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国副总理敦促在市场暴跌之际加大对上市公司的支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-vice-premier-urges-more-support-listed-firms-amid-market-rout-2024-01-29/</link><description>据新华社报道，在股市持续暴跌之际，中国国务院副总理何立峰周一呼吁加大对上市公司的支持，以帮助稳定资本市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 11:49:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-vice-premier-urges-more-support-listed-firms-amid-market-rout-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：在充满风险的一周中，降息押注胜过谨慎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view--2024-01-29/</link><description>内奥米·罗夫尼克 (Naomi Rovnick) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 11:05:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view--2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>面对 5G 部署缓慢，欧盟电信公司再次挑衅大型科技公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/faced-with-slow-5g-rollout-eu-telcos-single-out-big-tech-again-2024-01-29/</link><description>欧洲电信游说组织 ETNO 周一再次敦促大型科技公司帮助支付 5G 和宽带的部署费用，该组织发布的数据显示，欧洲在 5G 网络、云计算、投资和收入方面落后于美国和亚洲。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 11:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/faced-with-slow-5g-rollout-eu-telcos-single-out-big-tech-again-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国护照持有者可以免签前往哪些国家？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/which-countries-can-chinese-passport-holders-visit-without-visa-2024-01-29/</link><description>中国因新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 自我隔离三年，并于 2023 年重新开放边境，并与部分国家签署了免签证协议，以鼓励其公民旅行，这对吸引中国游客的外国目的地来说是一个福音。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:30:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/which-countries-can-chinese-passport-holders-visit-without-visa-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大承认香港法院的清算令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrande-acknowledges-hk-court-order-liquidate-2024-01-29/</link><description>中国恒大周一承认，香港法院下令对这家全球负债最重的房地产开发商进行清算，原因是该公司在拖欠债券两年多后未能提供具体的重组计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:09:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrande-acknowledges-hk-court-order-liquidate-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>对冲资金流 对冲基金以五年来最快速度买入中国股票 - 高盛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-hedge-funds-lap-up-china-stocks-fastest-pace-5-years-goldman-2024-01-29/</link><description>高盛在给客户的一份报告中写道，对冲基金上周三天内以五年多来最快的速度抢购遭受重创的中国股票。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:06:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-hedge-funds-lap-up-china-stocks-fastest-pace-5-years-goldman-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>由于立法行动陷入停滞，白宫人工智能委员会周一召开会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/white-house-ai-council-meets-monday-legislative-action-stalls-2024-01-29/</link><description>白宫人工智能委员会将于周一召开会议，三个月前，乔·拜登总统签署了一项旨在降低人工智能带来的风险的行政命令。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:04:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/white-house-ai-council-meets-monday-legislative-action-stalls-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国一月份工厂活动可能收缩，但幅度较小</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-january-factory-activity-likely-contracted-less-sharply-2024-01-29/</link><description>路透调查显示，中国 1 月份制造业活动可能连续第四个月萎缩，尽管增速较 12 月有所放缓，这表明该国庞大的制造业在 2024 年初仍难以恢复增长势头。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 09:02:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-january-factory-activity-likely-contracted-less-sharply-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾否认与中国有“特殊安排”向礁石上的部队提供补给</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-denies-special-arrangements-with-china-supply-troops-reef-2024-01-29/</link><description>菲律宾周一否认中国与马尼拉达成“临时特别安排”，允许向占领南海争议岛礁的菲律宾军队运送物资，称其为“凭空想象”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 08:58:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-denies-special-arrangements-with-china-supply-troops-reef-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促耗资数十亿美元的泰国铁路项目更快取得进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-faster-progress-billion-dollar-railway-link-thailand-2024-01-29/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周一表示，中国和泰国必须加快建设计划中的连接两国的高速铁路，推动雄心勃勃的东南亚网络。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 08:09:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-urges-faster-progress-billion-dollar-railway-link-thailand-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交部将认真研究恢复对日免签政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-foreign-ministry-will-seriously-study-resuming-visa-free-policy-japan-2024-01-29/</link><description>中国外交部周一表示，将“认真”研究恢复此前对日本游客赴华免签的安排。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 08:01:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-foreign-ministry-will-seriously-study-resuming-visa-free-policy-japan-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>内地与香港签署相互承认民商事案件安排</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hk-sign-arrangement-reciprocal-recognition-civil-commercial-cases-2024-01-29/</link><description>中国最高法院和香港律政司周一表示，双方签署了《关于两地相互认可和执行民商事案件判决的安排》，立即生效。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 07:21:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hk-sign-arrangement-reciprocal-recognition-civil-commercial-cases-2024-01-29/</guid></item><item><title>普洛斯资本为其中国收入基金 XII 筹集 14 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/glp-capital-partners-raises-14-bln-its-china-income-fund-xii-2024-01-29/</link><description>资产管理公司普洛斯资本周一表示，已与一家全球机构投资者合作，为其中国收益基金 XII 筹集 100 亿元人民币（合 14 亿美元），该基金将在中国拥有 25 个物流和商业园区。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 07:07:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/glp-capital-partners-raises-14-bln-its-china-income-fund-xii-2024-01-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>